<i>Puse cap la cap, faceau zero.</i>

115
00:10:03,767 --> 00:10:06,839
<i>Se pare ca nu eram capabil si gata.</i>

116
00:10:07,007 --> 00:10:10,886
<i>Venise timpul sa termin treaba</i>
<i>la Hollywood si sa ma duc acasa.</i>

117
