<i>Hopa!</i>

123
00:11:27,687 --> 00:11:30,759
<i>M- am trezit pe aleea</i>
<i>unei case impunatoare</i>

124
00:11:30,927 --> 00:11:33,646
<i>care parea veche si parasita.</i>

125
00:11:33,807 --> 00:11:36,560
<i>La capatul aleii, o priveliste frumoasa.</i>

126
00:11:36,727 --> 00:11:41,482
<i>Un garaj mare si gol,</i>
<i>stând fara nici un rost.</i>

127
00:11:41,647 --> 00:11:47,244
<i>Locul ideal unde sa pitesti</i>
<i>o masina cu probleme.</i>

128
00:11:55,167 --> 00:11:57,840
<i>În garajul ala mai era o masina.</i>

129
00:11:58,007 --> 00:12:00,919
<i>Un automobil enorm,</i>
<i>fabricat ín strainatate.</i>

130
00:12:01,087 --> 00:12:04,397
<i>Trebuie sa fi consumat</i>
<i>peste 20 de litri pe kilometru.</i>

131
